Package io.atlasmap.api

Interface AtlasSession

All Known Subinterfaces:
AtlasInternalSession
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultAtlasSession
public interface AtlasSession
Represents mapping processing session at runtime. This is supposed to be created for each execution through AtlasContext.
